caption.text:
"Fighting" arcrylic on 150x120 canvas 
First exibition at Taman Ismail Marzuki , 8-9  january 2016 
Concept:  The garuda character represents us as young generation fighting the globalization (represented by boxing match), however our mental are not strong enough and not ready yet.  Jokowi holding the right bullhead armor represents our president from PDIP. He's trying to empower us as future young leader to be able to withstand the upcoming challenge.  Jusuf Kalla holding the left banyan tree armor represents our vice president from GOLKAR. He sees right through the enemy eyes as he whisper "Understand your enemy!" Last but not least , i hope that we as the next generation, are able to guide this country wisely and bring us to better future which is represented as batik ciptoning.
